 * TESTING CHECKLIST:
 *
 * [ ] Unauthenticated user accessing /admin redirects to /login
 * [ ] Authenticated talent accessing /admin redirects to /
 * [ ] Authenticated admin can access /admin
 * [ ] Redirect parameter preserved (/login?redirect=/admin/submissions)
 * [ ] Session persists across page refreshes
 * [ ] Session auto-refreshes before expiry
 * [ ] Logout clears session and blocks access
 */
